title: UConn Football Vs. UCF
text:
Caption Jhavon Williams, Tyler Samra John Raoux / Associated Press Connecticut players, including cornerback Jhavon Williams (6) and offensive lineman Tyler Samra (60) celebrate as they hold up a rivalry trophy named by the team as the Conflict trophy after defeating Central Florida 40-13 in an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Orlando, Fla. The trophy is passed back and forth to the winner of the yearly game between Central Florida and Connecticut.

The trophy is passed back and forth to the winner of the yearly game between Central Florida and Connecticut.
